+    # ---------------------------------------------------------------------
+    # scan(self, filehandle, filename, fileformat)
+    # Ǽڵ带 ˻Ѵ.
+    # Է° : filehandle  -  ڵ
+    #         filename    -  ̸
+    #         fileformat  -  
